Preconditions:
- The length of the string `s` is greater than or equal to 1.
- The length of the integer array `shifts` is equal to the length of the string `s`.
- Each element in the integer array `shifts` is greater than or equal to 0.

Postconditions:
- The returned string is the final string after all shifts are applied.
- The length of the returned string is equal to the length of the input string `s`.
- Each character in the returned string is a lowercase English letter.